Maintainer: Lucas Gelape <lucas@voltdata.info>
Description: This package gives a set of functions to extract data from and conduct analysis 
    about [Brazil's News Atlas](https://atlas.jor.br/english/), an initiative that identifies 
    Brazilian news organizations, specially focused on local news. This package extracts data 
    available for free through the [API of the project](https://api.atlas.jor.br/docs).
